ing room or outside in the spacious yard and garden.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="wp-block-kadence-rowlayout alignnone"><div id="kt-layout-id_da825f-3b" class="kt-row-layout-inner kt-row-has-bg kt-layout-id_da825f-3b has-theme-palette-5-background-color"><div class="kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-1-columns kt-gutter-default kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-top kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row"><div class="wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1 kadence-column_692ca0-56"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><div class="wp-block-kadence-splitcontent aligncenter kt-sc_7a1c14-74"><div class="kt-split-content-wrap kt-sc-media-side-left" style="grid-template-columns:38% auto"><div class="kt-sc-imgcol kt-sc-imgcol-bg-auto kt-sc-img-side-left"><figure class="kt-split-content-media-image wp-image-container-33"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://comfortcarekf.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/hands-2906458_640.jpg" alt="loving-care-adult-foster-care" width="640" height="426" class="kt-split-content-img wp-image-33 lazyload"/><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://comfortcarekf.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/hands-2906458_640.jpg" alt="loving-care-adult-foster-care" width="640" height="426" class="kt-split-content-img wp-image-33 lazyload"/></noscript></figure></div><div class="kt-sc-textcol kt-sc-text-valign-center kt-sc-text-halign-center" style="min-height:450px"><div class="kt-sc-innter-col"><h5 class="kt-adv-heading_c4a688-28 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading has-theme-palette-8-color has-text-color" data-kb-block="kb-adv-heading_c4a688-28">What is Adult Foster Care</h5><p class="has-theme-palette-9-color has-text-color">Providing a supervised environment for adults that are unable to live independently. At Comfort Care We provide a safe environment for seniors that need additional assistance. Adult foster care homes provide a variety of services including:</p><div class="wp-block-kadence-rowlayout alignnone"><div id="kt-layout-id_95c2ab-88" class="kt-row-layout-inner kt-row-has-bg kt-layout-id_95c2ab-88 has-theme-palette-8-background-color"><div class="kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-2-columns kt-gutter-default kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-top kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row"><div class="wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1 kadence-column_0c374d-65"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><ul class="has-theme-palette-4-color has-text-color"><li>Assisting with daily personal care</li><li>Aiding in daily recreational activities</li><li>Providing transportation to medical appointments and other activities</li></ul></div></div><div class="wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-2 kadence-column_777dc9-89"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><ul class="has-theme-palette-4-color has-text-color"><li>Preparing and serving meals</li><li>Dispensing medications</li><li>Providing social interaction</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><ul class="has-theme-palette-4-color has-text-color"><li><a href="https://ltclicensing.oregon.gov/Facilities/Details/50R021" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Licensed facility </a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="wp-block-kadence-rowlayout alignnone"><div id="kt-layout-id_60e6d9-db" class="kt-row-layout-inner kt-row-has-bg kt-layout-id_60e6d9-db has-theme-palette-8-background-color"><div class="kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-2-columns kt-gutter-default kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-top kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-inherit kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row"><div class="wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1 kadence-column_28ee7c-4f"><div class="kt-inside-inner-col"><div id="kt-info-box_118558-7a" class="wp-block-kadence-infobox"><div class="kt-blocks-info-box-link-wrap kt-blocks-info-box-media-align-top kt-info-hali